column5: Just a reminder that Dave's new show, Fact's of Fishing, THE SHOW will be premiering tonight at 7 pm on WFN.  I have been waiting a while to see this one since I couldn't make the screening that a lucky few were able to attend... an hour and a half to go!!!  JP
